    <header class="site-header">
        <h1>The First Snowfall</h1>
        <p class="author">Written on [Date], by Your Loving Boyfriend</p>
    </header>

    <main class="poem-content">
        <pre>
The mountains wore their wedding white,
The day I saw your smile.
A sudden hush, a silver light,
That stopped me for a while.

Each flake a quiet, perfect peace,
Like moments spent with you.
A silent, beautiful release,
From everything I knew.

(Continue your poem here...)
